INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (5,3,'2013-07-15 23:34:29','2013-07-15 23:34:29','<p><span class=\"attn\">ATS is a team of agile experts</span> who are passionate about designing and developing custom software that creates direct connections between your data and your goals. From the US Navy and the Patent &amp; Trademark Office to power plants, sports leagues and more, we help organizations efficiently integrate, analyze and visualize the information they need to drive optimal performance, operational readiness and intelligent decisions.</p>','Home','','publish','open','closed','','home','','','2014-09-25 23:03:55','2014-09-25 23:03:55','',0,'http://dev.atsid.com/?page_id=5',1,'page','',0),(8,3,'2013-07-15 23:34:29','2013-07-15 23:34:29','','Home','','inherit','open','open','','5-revision-v1','','','2013-07-15 23:34:29','2013-07-15 23:34:29','',5,'http://dev.atsid.com/2013/07/15/5-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(15,3,'2013-12-23 06:48:40','2013-12-23 06:48:40','In 2012, our founder Melody had a nervous breakdown. Her business model had stopped working, her brand was being stolen out from under her, and she owed $60,000 that she didnt have. A speaker, author, and New York Times-featured serial entrepreneur who had run successful companies for more than 30 years, Melodys world started disintegrating.\r\n\r\nAfter six months of anxiety, desperation, and struggling to change out of her pajamas in the morning, friends started getting worried. After a year, they started getting really worried. Finally, a friend asked, Melody, what do you love?\r\n\r\nMarshmallows.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nFlashdance.\r\n\r\nThat was all it took.\r\n\r\n\r\nMarshmallow + Flashdance = ???\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nOver the next several months, Melody started having serendipitous conversations that made her think maybe there was something to thisa way to take failure, marshmallows, and Flashdance and put them together to change the trajectory of her lifeto move herself forward by moving other women forward.\r\n\r\nShe started putting the wheels in motion for the first Urban Campfire  an event in Seattle where women could actually talk about their failures and work through them to move forward together. It included not only Flashdance and marshmallows, but friendship, food trucks, and a bunch of women who needed to be vulnerable with each other and move forward in their lives.\r\n\r\nThat was in August. After the event, the letters started pouring in.\r\n\r\n\r\nHistory was made today in Seattle, in my soul, in my spirit and in my future. Thank you Urban Campfire for giving me exactly what I needed right now and for a day I will never forget. Bursting with joy, love of life and inspiration.\r\n\r\n\r\nUrban Campfire may have been one of the best nights of my life.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nSo. Effing. Awesome.\r\n\r\n\r\nMy heart and spirit are light and inspired today after immersing myself in the power and beauty present at Urban Campfire yesterday. What a bunch of kickass women. Lets do it again!!!\r\n\r\n\r\nConnecting like this  real heartfelt conversations  is SO what Ive been wanting more of. Thank you SO much for dreaming. &lt;3 Laurie\r\n\r\n\r\nThank you so much for yesterdays amazing Urban Campfire event! I was so impressed with the physical layout and location, the organization throughout the day, the quality of the speakers, the food trucks and liquid libations, and the opportunity to sit in a circle with other women in vulnerable conversations. It was great to see such creativity and whole-heartedness present.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nBEST EVENT EVER!!! xoxo Nicole\r\n\r\n\r\nIncredible. I feel so on fire.\r\n\r\n\r\nWhat an exciting and totally life-changing event yesterday was. I loved every minute and the women in my groups shared from their hearts and told stories that were full of courage, vulnerability, and openness.\r\n\r\n\r\nYesterday, I saw people all around me sitting there with that same sense of OH MY GOD. My life will be better forever because I was here today.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThen there were more letters. And more letters. Melody couldnt even look at them for two weeks because she was so overwhelmed by the response.\r\n\r\n\r\nSince then, word has spread, and weve had to figure out an answer to many questions, such as\r\n\r\nWhat now?\r\nHow do I keep this fire alive inside of me?\r\nHow can I share this with my friend who wasnt able to attend?\r\nHow can I meet more women like the ones who were at Urban Campfire?\r\nWhen do we get to do this again?\r\n\r\nIn response, we had an Urban Campfire Halloween event, which was amazing. Now were planning several winter events, in addition to the main Urban Campfire event to be held again in the summer of 2014. Were also putting together monthly CRAVE Fuel events in cities across the country. Were excited to get to have this amazing experience of connection and moving forward with more of you.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nBut theres been something missing. When were not at an Urban Campfire event (and for people who havent been able to attend one at all), its hard to keep that fire going. Life-as-usual starts getting in the way, and we lose the vision that all these amazing women reflect back to us at Urban Campfire. We forget the talks weve heard (and if you didnt get to attend, you never got to hear them in the first place). We have good intentions of following through, but we know we could be doing so much more if Urban Campfire was ongoing.\r\n\r\n\r\nNow were getting to the (even better) part.\r\nIn response to this desire for ongoing inspiration and connection, we created a new kind of online experience called Urban Campout, for all the times when were not at an inspirational, life-changing event. Urban Campout is for you if you want to develop real friendships with amazing women while getting incredible inspiration and tools to move forward in your life. Its for you if youve been to Urban Campfire and want to experience it again, with more context, and worksheets and action steps to help you follow through. Its also for you if youve never been to Urban Campfire and would like to experience an online version for the first time.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nWhether or not youve been to Urban Campfire, weve designed Urban Campout to help you:\r\n Re-align your life\r\n Get your mojo back\r\n Be inspired, every day\r\n Stay in touch with all you learned at Urban Campfire (or learn it all anew if youve never been)\r\n Make real friendships with kick-ass women who are doing kick-ass things\r\n Network! Without the horribleness.\r\n Get and maintain forward momentum in your life, business, and/or career\r\n\r\n\r\nMEMBERSHIP IN URBAN CAMPOUT INCLUDES:\r\n Immediate access to an online version of the 2013 Urban Campfire main-event, which weve turned\r\ninto a practical DIY program: Moving Past Failure and Fear: A 4-week course for discovering your\r\nbravest self. Includes vulnerable stories and life-affirming truth from some of the most inspiring folks\r\nwe know, including Danielle LaPorte, Agapi Stassinopoulos, Jen Louden, and more, plus a workbook to\r\nhelp you put what youre learning into practice. (normally $175)\r\n Ongoing access to digital programs birthed at our Urban Campfire events throughout the year\r\n(normally over $1,000 for one year of programs if you purchased these separately)\r\n A monthly theme + regular action steps from founder Melody Biringer to help you keep your forward\r\nmomentum throughout the year (normally $120 for one year)\r\n A friendly online environment where you can gather with friends youve met at Urban Campfire or\r\nCRAVE fuel events (and make new friends, even if youve never been) (normally $35 a month)\r\n Free passes to our monthly CRAVE Fuel events (if youre local), and video access to CRAVE Fuel if\r\nyoure not (normally $300 for a year of tickets if you paid at the door)\r\n Special early-bird pricing and registration for all Urban Campfire events (more than $300 off)\r\n\r\nCost of membership: $35/month\r\n\r\nJOIN THE CAMPOUT\r\n\r\n\r\nPremium Membership includes all of the above, plus:\r\n Hand-picked placement in a campfire circle  an intimate group of you and 9 other women, facilitated\r\nby a life coach (normally $150 a month)\r\n A group campfire circle call every month, led by your life coach (normally $150 a month)\r\n\r\nCost of premium membership: $135/month\r\n\r\nJOIN THE CAMPOUT\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nQUESTIONS WE THOUGHT YOU MIGHT ASK:\r\n\r\nWHAT HAPPENS WHEN I SIGN UP?\r\n Youll get an email that gives you immediate access to our exclusive Urban Campout website, with your\r\nown username and password\r\n Youll get access to your Getting Started guide, which will help you fill out your profile, start your CRAVE\r\nlist, get started with our course on Moving Past Failure and Fear, and meeting new friends\r\n Youll get your first monthly topic + action steps for the month (Januarys topic is VISION)\r\n Youll get email updates throughout the month whenever something new is happening on the site\r\nIf you are a premium member, youll also get:\r\n An email explaining how your campfire circle works\r\n In a few days (usually no more than two), youll also get an email letting you know which campfire circle\r\nand life coach youve been placed with, instructions on how to get to know your group, and a calendar\r\nwith the dates/times for your campfire circle calls each month\r\n\r\nWHY IS THIS SO INEXPENSIVE?\r\nSince the value of Urban Campout is so much more than the cost, we know it can seem kind of wonky. Why so cheap, when other programs cost several hundred dollars a month, or thousands of dollars a year? Our answer: we want to give this experience to as many women as we can. We have a vision for connection, vulnerability, and forward movement happening across the country. To facilitate that, weve included two different tiers, so its easy to participate.\r\n\r\nIS IT EASY TO CANCEL MY MEMBERSHIP?\r\nAbsolutely. You can do it right from your dashboard.\r\n\r\nHOW OFTEN ARE NEW COURSES RELEASED?\r\nWe are curating our events all across the country to create actionable programs that can keep you connected and moving forward. This year, we plan on producing at least 6 original digital programs, with more to come all the time.\r\n\r\nWe are so thrilled to be able to connect and motivate each other (and ourselves!) in this new way. We hope youll join us as we make 2014 the best year ever.\r\n\r\nJOIN AS A REGULAR MEMBER ($35/month)\r\n\r\nOR\r\n\r\nJOIN AS A PREMIUM MEMBER ($135/month)\r\n\r\nWeve got a spot saved for you, and we cant wait to see you there!','Home','','inherit','open','open','','5-revision-v1','','','2013-12-23 06:48:40','2013-12-23 06:48:40','',5,'http://dev.atsid.com/2013/12/23/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(16,3,'2013-12-23 06:49:34','2013-12-23 06:49:34','','Home','','inherit','open','open','','5-revision-v1','','','2013-12-23 06:49:34','2013-12-23 06:49:34','',5,'http://dev.atsid.com/2013/12/23/5-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(21,3,'2014-07-17 17:10:02','2014-07-17 17:10:02','<h2>Why Applied Technical Systems?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Applied Technical Systems Inc. (ATS) isan expert in cloud-based software solutions, lifecycle support solutions, data analytics, data mining and data visualization.We institute agile software development with user-centered design.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Founded in1980, ATS has helped government agencies and commercial clients arrive at better decisions through intelligent discovery solutions, total life cycle expertise for the US Navy, and a broad range of systems engineering services. ATS clients include the U.S. Intelligence Community, Department of Commerce, Department of Homeland Security, and the Department of Defense. Headquartered in Silverdale, WA, ATS also has offices in Alexandria and Suffolk, VA.<a title=\"History\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/meet-ats/history/\">Explore ATS History &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<div id=\"block-system-main\" class=\"block block-system block-main block-system-main even block-without-title\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n<div class=\"block-inner clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"content clearfix\">\r\n<article id=\"node-basic-page-72\" class=\"node node-basic-page node-published node-not-promoted node-not-sticky author-freelock odd clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n</article>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"block-views-portal-blocks-block\" class=\"block block-views block-portal-blocks-block block-views-portal-blocks-block odd block-without-title\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n<div class=\"block-inner clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"content clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"view view-portal-blocks view-id-portal_blocks view-display-id-block view-dom-id-c9bcdebffe61ace639b3db16bf9bc06a\">\r\n<div class=\"view-content\">\r\n<table class=\"views-view-grid cols-2\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"row-1 row-first\">\r\n<td class=\"col-1 col-first\">\r\n<div class=\"views-field views-field-title\">\r\n<h2><a title=\"Leadership\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/meet-ats/leadership/\">Leadership</a></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"views-field views-field-body\">\r\n<div class=\"field-content\">\r\n<p>Learn more about these salty and seasoned professionals that tirelessly strive to improve customer satisfaction.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"views-field views-field-field-block-link\">\r\n<div class=\"field-content more-link\"><a title=\"Leadership\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/meet-ats/leadership/\">&gt; view leadership</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td cl