\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Meet ATS','','publish','open','open','','meet-ats','','','2014-09-17 22:35:47','2014-09-17 22:35:47','',0,'http://dev.atsid.com/?page_id=21',2,'page','',0),(22,3,'2014-07-17 17:10:02','2014-07-17 17:10:02','','Meet ATS','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-v1','','','2014-07-17 17:10:02','2014-07-17 17:10:02','',21,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/07/17/21-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(23,3,'2014-07-17 17:10:11','2014-07-17 17:10:11','<h2>Specialized applications that connect data to decisions.</h2>\r\n<p>Our history of pioneering the development of data-driven, user-centered software has yielded a unique framework of technologies and applications that fulfill a variety of needs for diverse organizations, from traveling sports teams to nuclear power plants. This foundation provides a level of versatility and efficiency that enables us to bring highly tailored solutions to market quickly.</p>\r\n<p>ATS is a recognized leader in delivering high-end data analytics, software development services and a variety of logistics and maintenance solutions. We focus on understandingour customers requirements, so we can deliver solutions in an efficient and effective manner. Our expert staff is fully engaged in their work and empowered to find the most innovative technology solutionall driven by processes designed to maximize quality while controlling costs.</p>\r\n<h3><a title=\"TeamHub\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/products/team-hub/\">TeamHub</a></h3>\r\n<p>TeamHub takes the hassle out of event travel planning. It simplifies the coordination and execution of complex itineraries, organizes event-related information from players, and makes it easy to collaborate and manage team activities. </p>\r\n<h3><a title=\"Crew Atlas\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/products/crew-atlas/\">Crew Atlas</a></h3>\r\n<p>A comprehensive platform for utilities that provide tools and metrics to help power plants monitor, measure, manage, raise and improve crew performance.</p>\r\n<h3><a title=\"Crew Quiz\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/products/crew-quiz/\">Crew Quiz</a></h3>\r\n<p>Already noted as an industry best practice by site inspectors, Crew Quiz is an online Learning Management System (LMS) that enables a new level of interactive, computer-based training for operators acquiring or maintaining their license. </p>\r\n<h3><a title=\"MSAT\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/products/msat-explained/\">MSAT</a></h3>\r\n<p>The Maintenance Supportability Analysis Tool (MSAT) can deliver increased readiness, reduce system downtime, lower operational costs and increase Operational Availability (Ao).</p>\r\n<h3><a title=\"Arcus Search\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/products/arcus-search/\">Arcus Search</a></h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3><a title=\"Smithy\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/products/smithy/\">Smithy</a></h3>','Solutions','','publish','open','open','','products','','','2014-09-17 19:15:31','2014-09-17 19:15:31','',0,'http://dev.atsid.com/?page_id=23',3,'page','',0),(24,3,'2014-07-17 17:10:11','2014-07-17 17:10:11','','Products','','inherit','open','open','','23-revision-v1','','','2014-07-17 17:10:11','2014-07-17 17:10:11','',23,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/07/17/23-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(25,3,'2014-07-17 17:10:16','2014-07-17 17:10:16','<h2>ATS designs and develops custom software solutions that create direct connections between your data and your goals.</h2>\r\n<p>We help organizations integrate, analyze and visualize the data they need to power optimal performance, operational readiness and intelligent decisions.</p>\r\n<p>We are an experienced, cohesive team uniquely suited to resolving sophisticated business intelligence challenges from data engineering and analytics through user-centered interface design.</p>\r\n<p>ATS can help you realize value faster with our proven, proprietary technology framework and agile software development practices. However, the word agile describes more than just our approach to software development. Its the way we understand and respond to customers needs.</p>\r\n<h3><a title=\"Integrated Logistics Support\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/services/integrated-logistics-support/\">Integrated Logistics Support</a></h3>\r\n<p>MSAT is a tool that connects and visualizes disparate life cycle data to help decision makers drive system performance.</p>\r\n<h3><a title=\"Discovery and Decision Support\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/services/it-services/\">Discovery &amp; Decision Support</a></h3>\r\n<p>Are you frustrated with searching for value in large data sets? Do you spend a significant amount of time building complex data queries, but still can\'t find the information you need? Local or cloud-based Arcus data analytics software can help.</p>\r\n<h3><a title=\"Custom Software Development\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/services/software-development/\">Custom Software Development</a></h3>\r\n<p>ATS offers systems integration and custom software development that range from Web portals to data mining applications. Using agile software development we create user-centered designs that will enhance your business workflow.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','Services','','publish','open','open','','services','','','2014-10-08 16:56:16','2014-10-08 16:56:16','',0,'http://dev.atsid.com/?page_id=25',4,'page','',0),(26,3,'2014-07-17 17:10:16','2014-07-17 17:10:16','','Services','','inherit','open','open','','25-revision-v1','','','2014-07-17 17:10:16','2014-07-17 17:10:16','',25,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/07/17/25-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(27,3,'2014-07-17 17:10:30','2014-07-17 17:10:30','[caption id=\"attachment_136\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"213\"]<img class=\"wp-image-136 size-full\" src=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/businessman-shaking-hands.jpg\" alt=\"Join our team of valued clients and partners!\" width=\"213\" height=\"142\" /> Join our team of valued clients and partners![/c