ademarks.\r\n<div class=\"field field-name-field-link field-type-link-field field-label-hidden clearfix\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n<div class=\"field-items\">\r\n<div class=\"field-item even\"><a class=\"ext\" style=\"color: #8a2216;\" href=\"http://www.kitsapsun.com/news/2012/mar/19/silverdale-company-streamlining-patent-process/\">Silverdale company streamlining patent process</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"field field-name-field-date field-type-datetime field-label-hidden clearfix\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n<div class=\"field-items\">\r\n<div class=\"field-item even\"><span class=\"date-display-single\">Tuesday, March 20, 2012</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Silverdale company streamlining patent process','','publish','open','open','','silverdale-company-streamlining-patent-process','','','2014-07-18 18:34:54','2014-07-18 18:34:54','',0,'http://dev.atsid.com/?p=167',0,'post','',0),(169,3,'2014-07-18 18:32:31','2014-07-18 18:32:31','','CareyKolb','','inherit','open','open','','careykolb','','','2014-07-18 18:32:31','2014-07-18 18:32:31','',125,'http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/CareyKolb.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(170,3,'2014-07-18 18:32:56','2014-07-18 18:32:56','[caption id=\"attachment_169\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"213\"]<img class=\"wp-image-169 size-full\" src=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/CareyKolb.jpg\" alt=\"CareyKolb\" width=\"213\" height=\"142\" /> Carey Kolb talks about process modernization opportunities[/caption]\r\n<h3>Approached with a holistic, long-term objective in mind</h3>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nWhether we are developing custom software, or supporting your key IT systems we always take a step back and look at the big picture to understand interdependencies and long-term goals. This strategic approach ensures that we recommend the best way to meet your business or mission requirements while controlling costs and maximizing supportability across systems and processes into the future.\r\n\r\nW