ide operations personnel to serve aboard SBX-1.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">\"ATS is pleased to be recognized and awarded for our expertise and knowledge of Naval systems and operations,\" said Doug West, VP of ATSs Maintenance Support Group. Mr. West continues, \"ATS welcomes the opportunity to support Gryphon Technologies and the US Navy in the operation and sustainment of this critical operational asset of our Nations Ballistic Missile Defense System (BMDS).\"</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Along with ATS, the Gryphon Team also includes General Dynamics IT, Teledyne Brown Engineering, The GBS Group, KAYA Associates, The Parker Group, and Stimulus Engineering.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><em>Applied Technical Systems, Inc. (ATS) is an innovative data to decisions technology company with expertise in cloud computing, data analytics and Total Life Cycle Systems Management (TLCSM). Since 1980, ATS has been providing system lifecycle support solutions and software engineering services that help streamline operations, improve operational performance and lower costs. Headquartered in Silverdale, Washington, ATS also has offices in McLean, Virginia and Suffolk, Virginia. For more information about ATS, visit<a style=\"color: #8a2216;\" href=\"http://www.atsid.com/\">http://www.atsid.com</a>or call 360.698.7100.</em></p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Media Contact:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Doug West\nApplied Technical Systems, Inc.\n757.483.5959\n<a class=\"mailto\" style=\"color: #8a2216;\" href=\"mailto:doug.west@atsid.com\">doug.west@atsid.com</a>\n<a style=\"color: #8a2216;\" href=\"http://www.atsid.com/\">www.atsid.com</a></p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">C.J. Davis\nGryphon Technologies, L.C.\n240.387.1000x 220\n<a class=\"mailto\" style=\"color: #8a2216;\" href=\"mailto:CDavis@GryphonLC.com\">CDavis@GryphonLC.com</a>\n<a class=\"ext\" style=\"color: #8a2216;\" href=\"http://www.gryphonlc.com/\">