\n<h3>Get a demo of MSAT today</h3>\r\n<a style=\"color: #8a2216;\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/meet-ats/contact-us/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/request-demo2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"45\" /></a>','MSAT Explained','','inherit','open','open','','254-revision-v1','','','2014-07-18 19:22:53','2014-07-18 19:22:53','',254,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/07/18/254-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(259,3,'2014-07-18 19:23:56','2014-07-18 19:23:56','<iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/CHj8gIbiP40\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">MSAT is a tool that connects and visualizes disparate life cycle data to help decision makers drive system performance.</span>\r\n<h3>Get a demo of MSAT today</h3>\r\n<a style=\"color: #8a2216;\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/meet-ats/contact-us/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/request-demo2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"45\" /></a>','MSAT Explained','','inherit','open','open','','254-revision-v1','','','2014-07-18 19:23:56','2014-07-18 19:23:56','',254,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/07/18/254-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(260,3,'2014-07-18 19:27:44','2014-07-18 19:27:44','<h2>Readiness solutions for both fielded and troubled systems</h2>\r\n<p>Most onboard logistics support problems can be traced to technical data problems. The lack of integration between engineering, maintenance and logistics support data is a well-known, ongoing issue that reduces Operational Availability (Ao)for the Navy.</p>\r\n<p>For over 30 years, ATS has provided preventative and corrective maintenance support solutions to its customers. ATS is the first company that can show technical data errors between relevant engineering, maintenance and logistics data and provide its customers with a maintenance sustainment solution that correctsthis systemic data integration problemfrom the deck-plate to the SYSCOM level.</p>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_285\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"213\"]<a href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/msc1.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-285 size-full\" src=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/msc1.png\" alt=\"Maintenance Support Center Data Analysis\" width=\"213\" height=\"142\" /></a> Maintenance Support Center Data Analysis[/caption]\r\n\r\n<p>Too often there are serious problems with maintenance support, particularly onboard repair parts, but the root cause of these problems is seldom evident to shipboard techniciansthey just learn to live with them. Our technicians, however, are specially trained to troubleshoot and fix these logistics support system problems in much the same way as shipboard technicians are trained to troubleshoot and fix shipboard system problems. Our expertise and services in this area include:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Engineering, Maintenance and Logistic Data interrelation analysis using our <a title=\"MSAT\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/products/msat-explained/\">Maintenance and SupportabilityAnalysis Tool (MSAT)</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>System Sustainment Solutions</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Maintenance Support Solutions</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Maintenance Failure Root Cause Analysis and Solutions</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Supply Support Analysis and Solutions</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Technical Data Quality Assurance</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Acquisition Support Analysis and Solutions</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>Operational Availability (Ao) Analysis and Solutions</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><a title=\"MSAT\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/products/msat-explained/\">Maintenance and Supportability Analysis Tool (MSAT)</a></h3>\r\n<p>ATS pioneered the solution to Navy\'s problem by developing a unique data correlation system that allows us to integrate this data through a common configuration structure. MSAT has the capability to ingest any type of engineering, maintenance and logistics support data down to the piece part level in order to automatically expose and eliminate the data disconnects thatcreate or contribute to deck plate logistics support problems.<a title=\"MSAT\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/products/msat-explained/\">Learn more about MSAT</a>.</p>\r\n<p>The sole function of an integrated logistics support solution is to facilitate efficient and effective execution of system maintenance functions. The only way to truly measure the effectiveness of these products (and the processes behind them) is to analyze actual system failures to see how well the logistics support system supported the maintenance action.To do this,logistics support analysts need to take a close look at all maintenance actions to determine exactly what failed, what logistics support was required to restore the system, and whether or not that support was readily identifiable and available to the system technician.Finding and fixing the root cause of these problems is what ATS does best.</p>\r\n<p>ATS can help you outline a sustainment strategy/plan to deliver increased readiness and availability.<strong> <a href=\"http://atsid.com/contact-us?interest=msat-demo\">Contact ATS</a> </strong>todayto learn more about our in-depth Maintenance and Readiness Support Services.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3></h3>','Maintenance and Supportability Analysis','','publish','open','open','','maintenance-and-supportability-analysis','','','2014-09-16 22:04:02','2014-09-16 22:04:02','',120,'http://dev.atsid.com/?page_id=260',0,'page','',0),(261,3,'2014-07-18 19:27:04','2014-07-18 19:27:04','<h3>Third data patent for relational graphing analysis engine</h3>\r\n<strong>Silverdale, Wash. - Jan. 5, 2012</strong>- Applied Technical Systems (ATS) has announced that the United States Patent and Trademark Office has issued a patent for an innovative cellular-like data model to describe and relate complex data structures, perform distributed data analy