s and other battle group vessels:\r\n<ul style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n	<li>Maintenance Support Center (MSC)</li>\r\n	<li>Integrated Logistic Support (ILS)</li>\r\n	<li>Acquisition and Life Cycle Management Services for Command, Control, Communications, Computers, Combat Systems, Intelligence, Surveillance, and Reconnaissance (C5ISR), Hull, Mechanical and Electrical (HM&amp;E) and shipboard Aviation Systems.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">ATS is comprised of maintenance technicians and data integration experts. ATS brings a unique approach to any systems engineering effort by ensuring a key focus area is product or systemlifecycle supportability and maintainability within the existing infrastructure of the business or organization. ATS hires maintenance technicians that have operated and maintained systems and equipment. We then train them in our logistic supportprocedures that were the basis of the Integrated Shipboard Maintenance Support (ISMS) training developed by ATS over 25 years ago and still maintained today. By hiring personnel already familiar with systems and equipment, we have personnel that can easily communicate with any other technician we come in contact with about systems  with an advantage  our personnel also understand the ins and outs of logistics support systems and logistics solutions.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>ATS Integrated Logistic Support services include but are not limited to the following:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n	<li>System Configuration Identification &amp; Validation - System Diagrammatics - Configuration Item / Technical Information (CI-TI) Database Development - System Failure Analysis - Preventative Maintenance / Supportability Analysis - Ship Change Document (SCD)/Non-SCD Identification and Tracking</li>\r\n	<li>Integrated Logistic Support Troubleshooting and Repair</li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"ILS Support &amp; Training\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/our-solutions/lifecycle-support-solutions/ils-support-training/\">Technical &amp; Logistics Training</a></li>\r\n	<li><a title=\"ILS Systems Support\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/our-solutions/lifecycle-support-solutions/ils-support-training/ils-systems-support/\">Integrated Logistic Support Systems Support</a>(e.g. ICAPS, CDMD-OA, OMMS-NG, etc.)</li>\r\n	<li>Business Process and Workflow Automation</li>\r\n	<li>DoDAF Modeling Support</li>\r\n	<li>Software/Database Development</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/meet-ats/contact-us/\">Contact ATS today</a>to learn more about our Integrated Logistic Support services and other logistics solutions.</p>','ILS Support & Training','','inherit','open','open','','293-revision-v1','','','2014-07-18 21:42:44','2014-07-18 21:42:44','',293,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/07/18/293-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(312,3,'2014-07-18 21:46:55','2014-07-18 21:46:55','<aside class=\"alignright\">\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_294\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"213\"]<img class=\"wp-image-294 size-full\" src=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/msc3.png\" alt=\"msc3\" width=\"213\" height=\"142\" /> ATS and the US Navy in the MSC[/caption]\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_295\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"213\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-295\" src=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/underway_0.jpg\" alt=\"Keeping our fleet afloat and ready since 1980\" width=\"213\" height=\"142\" /> Keeping our fleet afloat and ready since 1980[/caption]\r\n\r\n</aside>\r\n<h3>Arming the maintenance and support community with the latest logistics support knowledge and logistics system processes</h3>\r\nFor over 30 years, ATS has provided our US Navy with the highest level of Integrated Logistics Support(ILS) to ensure our ships are ready to set sea. ATS presently provides the followinglogistics supportservices to all COMNAVAIRPAC (CNAP) / COMNAVAIRLANT (CNAL) aircraft carriers and other battle group