 Operational Availability (Ao) and system sustainability problems experienced by the fleet today can be traced to a failure somewhere in the shore-based lifecycle logistics support system. Lack of onboard repair parts (OBRP) supply support is a particularly acute system sustainability problem, but there are also systemic problems with technical manuals, drawings, configuration and other types of engineering technical data. In many cases these technical data problems are the root cause of OBRP support problems, but they are often perceived as a Supply support problem.</p>\r\n<p>ATS uses our unique product lifecycle maintenance solutions to troubleshoot and correct lifecycle integrated logistics support and sustainability problems. Most of our Maintenance Support Group technicians are former Navy technicians who have extensive experience in the operation and maintenance of the full spectrum of shipboard systems. This maintenance-oriented perspective is fundamental to our view of the integrated logistics support world and our maintenance support analysis processes.</p>\r\n<p>We train our maintenance support technicians using our own in-house lifecycle support management training program which we developed from years of hands on experience in all facets of the integrated logistics support system. The end result is an experienced shipboard maintenance technician who is also trained to troubleshoot and repair any element of the Navys integrated logistics support system to make sure the ILS system provides our sailors with the parts, data and tools they need to restore failed systems with minimal delay.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" align=\"left\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">\r\n<h2>Maintenance &amp; Supportability Analysis</h2>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<h2>Configuration Data Management (CDM)</h2>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>ATS has provided preventative and corrective maintenance support solutions to its customers for over 30 years. Analyzing system failures, maintenance actions and technical data that drive logistics support solutions.&gt; <a title=\"Maintenance and Supportability Analysis\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/our-solutions/lifecycle-support-solutions/maintenance-and-supportability-analysis/\">read more on Maintenance and Supportability</a></td>\r\n<td>CDM is a discipline applied to a Configuration Item for its entire lifecycle - defining system configuration with progressive purification. Effective CDM ensures that the defined user requirements of a Configuration Item are met.&gt; <a title=\"Configuration Data Management\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/our-solutions/lifecycle-support-solutions/configuration-data-management/\">read more on Configuration Data Management</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<h2>Product Lifecycle Management (PLM)</h2>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<h2>ILS Support &amp; Training</h2>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>We can deliver a single, authoritative source for product and lifecycle data. Let ATS help you harness the power of Product Lifecycle Management (PLM) processes and systems that can transform your current processes.&gt; <a title=\"Product Lifecycle Management\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/our-solutions/lifecycle-support-solutions/product-lifecycle-management/\">read more on Product Lifecycle Management</a></td>\r\n<td>For over 30 years, ATS has provided our US Navy with the highest level of Integrated Logistics Support providing fleet support, training and assistance during technology insertion.&gt;<a title=\"ILS Support &amp; Training\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/our-solutions/lifecycle-support-solutions/ils-support-training/\">read more on Integrated Logistics Support</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','Resource Lifecycle Management  ','','inherit','open','open','','120-revision-v1','','','2014-08-06 18:15:50','2014-08-06 18:15:50','',120,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/08/06/120-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(523,3,'2014-08-06 18:19:04','2014-08-06 18:19:04',' ','','','publish','open','open','','523','','','2014-09-17 22:20:45','2014-09-17 22:20:45','',25,'http://dev.atsid.com/?p=523',18,'nav_menu_item','',0),(524,3,'2014-08-06 18:19:04','2014-08-06 18:19:04',' ','','','publish','open','open','','524','','','2014-09-17 22:20:45','2014-09-17 22:20:45','',25,'http://dev.atsid.com/?p=524',17,'nav_menu_item','',0),(525,3,'2014-08-06 18:19:04','2014-08-06 18:19:04',' ','','','publish','open','open','','525','','','2014-09-17 22:20:45','2014-09-17 22:20:45','',25,'http://dev.atsid.com/?p=525',16,'nav_menu_item','',0),(526,3,'2014-08-06 18:19:43','2014-08-06 18:19:43','<aside class=\"alignright\">\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_342\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"213\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-342\" src=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/qualityassurance-1.jpg\" alt=\"Quality Assurance\" width=\"213\" height=\"142\" /> Quality Assurance[/caption]\r\n<br />\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_343\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"213\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-343\" src=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/swe-1.jpg\" alt=\"Collaborative Development\" width=\"213\" height=\"142\" /> Collaborative Development[/caption]\r\n<br />\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_344\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"213\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-344\" src=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/whiteboard2-1.jpg\" alt=\"Continuous Engineering\" width=\"213\" height=\"142\" /> Continuous Engineering[/caption]\r\n</aside>\r\n<h3>Agile Software Development - experts in data</h3>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">ATS is a top software development company that specializes in agile software development. We leverage our attention to user-centered software design and our long history of expertise in data to develop custom software that enhances workflow and the overall effectiveness of the user.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">ATS offers a breadth and depth of services in systems integration and custom software development that range from Web portals to data mining applications. We specialize in helping customers extract valuable information from complex, high-volume databases, and have developed several groundbreaking, patented sofwaretechnologies in this area.</p>\r\n<h3>Engaged to innovate and deliver exceptional results</h3>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">We are as adept at integrating commercially available software into a solution as developing custom code, and apply the same vigor of process to both endeavors. Our first-class team ofsoftware developershas a wide range of skills and certifications, and a common goalto design, develop and deploy innovative solutions that affordably meet their customers needs both today, and in the future.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">All of our engagements begin with a detailed discovery and analysis phase that takes into account requirements, system interdependencies, and long-term sustainability. Combining this strategic approach with a team of the industrys best and brightest systems and software developers enables us to produce exceptional results for our customers.</p>\r\n<h3>Capabilities spanning the entire software development life cycle</h3>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Our capabilities in this area span all phases of the software development and integration process and include:</p>\r\n<table style=\"color: #000000;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><b>Discovery &amp; Analysis</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Design &amp; Development</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Detailed requirements gathering</li>\r\n<li>Extensive stakeholder interviews</li>\r\n<li>Workflow mapping</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>User-centered, iterative design</li>\r\n<li>Rapid software prototyping</li>\r\n<li>UI and quality testing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><b>Deployment &amp; Training</b></td>\r\n<td><b>Optimization &amp; Maintenance</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Phased software rollout</li>\r\n<li>Onsite and online training</li>\r\n<li>Documentation authoring</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Feedback gathering</li>\r\n<li>System enhancements</li>\r\n<li>Maintenance &amp; upgrades</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/meet-ats/contact-us/\">Contact ATS today</a>to discuss your next software development project.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"></p>','Custom Software Engineering','','inherit','open','open','','171-revision-v1','','','2014-08-06 18:19:43','2014-08-06 18:19:43','',171,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/08/06/171-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(527,3,'2014-08-06 18:22:39','2014-08-06 18:22:39','<aside class=\"alignright\">\r\n<p>[caption id=\"attachment_322\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"200\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-322\" src=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/HPIM1383-sm.jpg\" alt=\"ATS adopts a road in Suffolk, VA\" width=\"200\" height=\"163\" /> ATS adopts a road in Suffolk, VA[/caption]</p>\r\n<p>[caption id=\"attachment_323\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"200\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-323\" src=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/e-d-sm.jpg\" alt=\"Charity event with Congressman Dicks\" width=\"200\" height=\"134\" /> Charity event with Congressman Dicks[/caption]</p>\r\n<p>[caption id=\"attachment_324\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"200\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-324\" src=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/31Heroes-sm.jpg\" alt=\"31 Heroes Fundraiser\" width=\"200\" height=\"131\" /> 31 Heroes Fundraiser[/caption]</p>\r\n</aside>\r\n<h3>Outstanding People + Innovative Technology = Exceptional Results</h3>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Every day the work at ATS has a direct impact on the day-to-day productivity of federal agencies and businesses across the nation. We play key roles in innovative ideas and concepts to deliver results that will shape our future.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Our employees are experts who challenge each other to grow as part of a productive team. They aren\'t stuck working just one aspect of the job... they have their hands on a variety of projects. It\'s a small company and each of our employees\' skills directly influences the company\'s success.</p>\r\n<h3>Software Development</h3>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Our engineers tackle some of the most complex challenges in large-scale computing with vast amounts of data. Software development engineers, technical program managers, test engineers, and user-interface experts work in small teams company-wide to contribute to the productivity of organizations that include:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n<li>Intelligence Community</li>\r\n<li>Department of Commerce</li>\r\n<li>US Navy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Systems-oriented Technicians and Engineers</h3>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Our team of program managers, maintenance technicians, data analysts, and engineers analyze the performance of systems critical to our nations defense and do the necessary actions to ensure their operational availability and mission capability.</p>\r\n<h3>Top 10 Reasons to work at ATS</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Solve complex problems.</strong>There are hundreds of challenges yet to solve. Your creative ideas matter here and are worth exploring. Youll have the opportunity to develop innovative new products that people all over the world will find useful.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Innovation is our DNA.</strong>Even the best technology can be improved. We see endless opportunity to create even more relevant, more useful, and faster products for our users.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Commitment to Excellence</strong>. We do this for our customers and for each other because we believe in doing the right thing right, and in that order!</li>\r\n<li><strong>Appreciation is the best motivation</strong>. Weve created a fun and inspiring workspace youll be glad to be a part of, including professional development opportunities, recognition for hard work and extra effort, and plenty of opportunities to shine.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Work and play are not mutually exclusive.</strong>It is possible to code and pass the puck at the same time.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Family First</strong>. Our customers become friends and our employees are our extended family!</li>\r\n<li><strong>We love our employees, and we want them to know it.</strong>ATS offers a variety of benefits, including a choice of medical programs, company-matched 401(k), flexible work schedules, bonus program, and much more.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Personal Development</strong>. We believe that a happy, successful you is in the best interest of everyone here at ATS. We want you to be a happy, motivated leader and well do everything we can to help you reach your personal career goals.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Employee Appreciation Events</strong>. In addition to a variety of BBQs and fantastic holiday parties, Employee of the Quarter, iPad incentive program, and bonus plan ATS uses the third Thursday of each month to get together and share whats good</li>\r\n<li><strong>Promising Future.</strong>ATS has been around for over 30 years and we believe the best years are yet to come!</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Company headquarters is located in beautiful Silverdale, Washington (just a ferry ride away from Seattle). The idyllic setting lies between two mountain ranges and is just a few minutes\' drive to Puget Sound. We also have offices located in the vibrant metro areas of Alexandria and Suffolk, Virginia.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>What Our Employees Are Saying:</strong></p>\r\n<table style=\"color: #000000;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>ATS makes sure I have the tools I need to get the job done. If I have a problem with the equipment, it\'s fixed immediately. If I need to use a particular piece of software to get a job done, I can get it.<strong>- Bryan B., Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-bryan.benson-small.png\" alt=\"Bryan B.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-travis.towne-small.png\" alt=\"Travis T.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n<td>ATS is not only the company I work for; theyre my future, my life, and my career. <strong>- Travis T., Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>Working here is unique. While celebrating success is a common theme for most companies, its also true at ATS that failure is not scored, but learned from.<strong>- James M., Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-james.mello-small.png\" alt=\"James M.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-bill.peterson-small.png\" alt=\"Bill P.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n<td>I came back to work at ATS because this company is an example of how to do things right. Treat your employees with respect and compassion, and they\'ll make sure the customers are happy and the job is well done.<strong>- Bill P., Assessments Lead</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>I get a chance to fly on and off of an aircraft carrier in a plane. That was a unique experience in itself and better than any roller coaster. I work in an exciting field for a great company with fantastic people! How much better can it get?<strong></strong><strong>- Kevin S.,</strong><strong>Senior Configuration Analyst</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-lacy.dove-small.png\" alt=\"Lacy D.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n<td>I enjoy working at ATS because I love the people, the attitudes, the flexible schedule, the diverse work opportunities, and the feeling of being valued.-<strong>Lacy D., Senior Project Coordinator</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>After spending time with a larger more bureaucratic (slower decision making) company, I found that the ATS business model best allowed me to support customers. Many folks that I have been working with have been here for 10-15 and over 20 years  that says something about a company.-<strong>Doug W., Vice President</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-doug.west-small.png\" alt=\"Doug W.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>ATS cares more for its employees than any company I have ever worked for.<strong>- Dan H., Senior Configuration Analyst</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>Of all the places I have worked, none of them made me feel at home and as valuable at the same time as the team here at ATS.<strong>- Isaac F., Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-isaac.flemming-small.png\" alt=\"Isaac F.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-aaron.moore-small.png\" alt=\"Aaron M.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n<td>ATS sets a standard; I get to work with people who truly care about the quality of their work and communication.<strong>- Aaron M., Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>Every employee is working together to make each project a success. ATS is not only Data to Decisions, but people to decisions.-<strong>Matthew L.,</strong><strong>Recruiting Coordinator</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-matt.linkemyer-small.png\" alt=\"Matt L.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-bryan.benson-small.png\" alt=\"Bryan B.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n<td>I am able to learn every facet of this project and work with numerous technologies beyond Java.<strong>- Bryan B., Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td><b></b>I decided to come to ATS because not only is it closer to home, but I got more of a family feeling here. I felt as though my contributions would be better recognized than they would if I was just another cog in a much larger machine.<strong>- Jim W., QA Lead</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-jim.wingren-small.png\" alt=\"Jim W.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>\"ATS is a great place to work. Located far away from the maddening big city, traffic makes getting to work easy. Working with great people and a company that cares about individuals makes staying at work enjoyable.\"<strong>-Eric M.</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-pushpinder.heer-small.png\" alt=\"Pushpinder H.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n<td>The team comradery that exists at ATS is like no other. Employees at every level truly love and understand their role.<strong>-Pushpinder H., Software Engineer III</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>I like working for ATS because upper management really wants to create something useful for the customer. They genuinely want to solve real problems for the Navy,not just make money. That makes me feel good about working here.<strong>- Rick W., Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>I like working at ATS because the CEO is such a great guy<strong></strong><strong>- Rick L., President &amp; CEO</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-rick.leenstra-small.png\" alt=\"Rick L.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-bob.lawing-small.png\" alt=\"Bob L.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n<td>\"They look out for their troops; they are straight forward and honest. Management is good at acquiring work.\"-<strong>Bob L., Senior Configuration Specialist</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>\"I love being able to be myself, yet always being challenged to better myself.\"<strong>- Aaron M., Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-aaron.moore-small.png\" alt=\"Aaron M.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #3c3c3c;\"><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-eric.portney-small.png\" alt=\"Eric P.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #3c3c3c;\">\"ATS has assembled a dynamic, experienced group of individuals who understand how to work together as a team, how to approach problems in innovative ways, and who arent afraid to try bold solutions.\"</span><strong>- Eric P., Proposal Coordinator</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\"ATS has the funniest, most interesting white boards of anywhere I\'ve worked. Where else would you find a white board showing the design for a flux capacitor?\"</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>- Bryan B., Software Engineer</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-bryan.benson-small.png\" alt=\"Bryan B.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-lacy.dove-small.png\" alt=\"Lacy D.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n<td>\"The diversity of my work allows me to work with many people, across several projects, covering a wide array of tasks so Im seldom bored. We like to work, learn and socialize together... and that makes all the difference.\"<strong>- Lacy D., Senior Project Coordinator</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>\"As an ATS employee, you are part of the family.\"<strong>- Dennis W., Director</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-dennis.wilkelis-small.png\" alt=\"Dennis W.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>\"Working at ATS has put me in direct contact with not only some of the finest minds working in technology today, but also some of the finest people you would ever want to meet. Cutting edge thinkers meet cutting edge technology, what\'s better than that?\"<strong>- Devin W., Systems Administrator</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','Our Culture','','inherit','open','open','','320-revision-v1','','','2014-08-06 18:22:39','2014-08-06 18:22:39','',320,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/08/06/320-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(528,3,'2014-08-06 18:22:56','2014-08-06 18:22:56','<aside class=\"alignright\">\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_338\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"213\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-338\" src=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/2.jpg\" alt=\"College Interns Mackenzie, Jamison and Mitchell\" width=\"213\" height=\"142\" /> College Interns Mackenzie, Jamison and Mitchell[/caption]</p>\r\n<p>[caption id=\"attachment_339\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"213\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-339\" src=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/3.jpg\" alt=\"Kate Wilson and Chris Prince (R&amp;D Lead)\" width=\"213\" height=\"142\" /> Kate Wilson and Chris Prince (R&amp;D Lead)[/caption]<br />\r\n</aside>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Applied Technical Systems is looking for talentedindividuals in high school or college, interested insoftware development. ATS offers students theopportunity to expand their knowledge-base indeveloping web software, Java and JavaScriptdevelopment, User Interface design, QualityAssurance, and Project Coordination.</p>\r\n<h2>High School Internships</h2>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Our high school interns start out conducting quality assurance tests on one of ATSs major software applications. High school interns may potentially receive small coding projects to experience the task of development at an industry level while meeting time constraints.</p>\r\n<h2>College Internships</h2>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Our college interns have the opportunity to work cooperatively with an appointed mentor on current ATS projects while gaining further experience using the latest computer technologies.</p>\r\n<h2>Our Interns come from colleges and universities around the country</h2>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Past Interns have attended these prestigious colleges and we are always interested in expanding our network!</p>\r\n<ul style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n<li>University of Washington</li>\r\n<li>Washington State University</li>\r\n<li>Iowa State University</li>\r\n<li>Carnegie Mellon University</li>\r\n<li>Stanford University</li>\r\n<li>Harding University</li>\r\n<li>Brigham Young University</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<table style=\"color: #000000;\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">\r\n<h2>Requirements:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Have a 3.0 GPA or higher</li>\r\n<li>Interested in computer science and technology</li>\r\n<li>Must be a United States citizen</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"50%\">\r\n<h2>Example Intern Projects:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Programming JavaScript Modules</li>\r\n<li>iPad Application Development</li>\r\n<li>Quality Assurance</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h2>Testimonials from our Mentors:</h2>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">\"For a number of years I have worked with the interns at ATS. They each bring their own unique gifts and walk away with a skill set that can be used for future employment. We have had our interns go on to work at great companies like Google, as well as some who have come back to become leaders and mentors here at ATS. The internship program here at ATS is a great way to get experience and challenge yourself.\"<br />\r\n<strong>- Chris Prince, Research &amp; Development Lead</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">I believe the intern program is a way to foster the next generation of young IT professionals in a fun and collaborative environment. The moment they start at ATS, our interns become a part of a team and add to the culture and success of the company. They are fun-loving, driven, and hungry for experience and arent afraid to fail in order to succeed. We want our interns to leave successful with the hope that they will eventually want to come back.<br />\r\n<strong>- Lacy Dove, Senior Project Coordinator</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">\r\n<h3>Start your experience at ATS today!</h3>\r\n<p><a style=\"color: #8a2216;\" href=\"http://atsid.hrmdirect.com/employment/job-opening.php?req=81262&amp;&amp;nohd#job\"><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/atsid-button-apply.png\" alt=\"Apply\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\r\n','Intern Program','','inherit','open','open','','337-revision-v1','','','2014-08-06 18:22:56','2014-08-06 18:22:56','',337,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/08/06/337-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(529,3,'2014-08-06 18:40:23','2014-08-06 18:40:23','<div>\r\n<p>Look for ATS at these upcoming Conferences &amp; Trade Shows.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<table>\r\n<thead>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>Date</th>\r\n<th>Event</th>\r\n<th>Location</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>July 27, 2014</td>\r\n<td><a title=\"Whaling Days / Silverdale Rotary Duck Race\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/meet-ats/meetings-events/whaling-days-silverdale-rotary-duck-race/\">Whaling Days / Silverdale Rotary Duck Race</a></td>\r\n<td>Silverdale Waterfront ParkSilverdale WA 98383</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n','Meetings & Events','','inherit','open','open','','84-revision-v1','','','2014-08-06 18:40:23','2014-08-06 18:40:23','',84,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/08/06/84-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(530,3,'2014-08-06 18:42:38','2014-08-06 18:42:38','<p style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>What Our Employees Are Saying:</strong></p>\r\n<table style=\"color: #000000;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>ATS makes sure I have the tools I need to get the job done. If I have a problem with the equipment, it\'s fixed immediately. If I need to use a particular piece of software to get a job done, I can get it.<strong>- Bryan B., Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-bryan.benson-small.png\" alt=\"Bryan B.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-travis.towne-small.png\" alt=\"Travis T.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n<td>ATS is not only the company I work for; theyre my future, my life, and my career. <strong>- Travis T., Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>Working here is unique. While celebrating success is a common theme for most companies, its also true at ATS that failure is not scored, but learned from.<strong>- James M., Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-james.mello-small.png\" alt=\"James M.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-bill.peterson-small.png\" alt=\"Bill P.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n<td>I came back to work at ATS because this company is an example of how to do things right. Treat your employees with respect and compassion, and they\'ll make sure the customers are happy and the job is well done.<strong>- Bill P., Assessments Lead</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>I get a chance to fly on and off of an aircraft carrier in a plane. That was a unique experience in itself and better than any roller coaster. I work in an exciting field for a great company with fantastic people! How much better can it get?<strong></strong><strong>- Kevin S.,</strong><strong>Senior Configuration Analyst</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-lacy.dove-small.png\" alt=\"Lacy D.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n<td>I enjoy working at ATS because I love the people, the attitudes, the flexible schedule, the diverse work opportunities, and the feeling of being valued.-<strong>Lacy D., Senior Project Coordinator</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>After spending time with a larger more bureaucratic (slower decision making) company, I found that the ATS business model best allowed me to support customers. Many folks that I have been working with have been here for 10-15 and over 20 years  that says something about a company.-<strong>Doug W., Vice President</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-doug.west-small.png\" alt=\"Doug W.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>ATS cares more for its employees than any company I have ever worked for.<strong>- Dan H., Senior Configuration Analyst</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>Of all the places I have worked, none of them made me feel at home and as valuable at the same time as the team here at ATS.<strong>- Isaac F., Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-isaac.flemming-small.png\" alt=\"Isaac F.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-aaron.moore-small.png\" alt=\"Aaron M.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n<td>ATS sets a standard; I get to work with people who truly care about the quality of their work and communication.<strong>- Aaron M., Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>Every employee is working together to make each project a success. ATS is not only Data to Decisions, but people to decisions.-<strong>Matthew L.,</strong><strong>Recruiting Coordinator</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-matt.linkemyer-small.png\" alt=\"Matt L.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-bryan.benson-small.png\" alt=\"Bryan B.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n<td>I am able to learn every facet of this project and work with numerous technologies beyond Java.<strong>- Bryan B., Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td><b></b>I decided to come to ATS because not only is it closer to home, but I got more of a family feeling here. I felt as though my contributions would be better recognized than they would if I was just another cog in a much larger machine.<strong>- Jim W., QA Lead</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-jim.wingren-small.png\" alt=\"Jim W.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>\"ATS is a great place to work. Located far away from the maddening big city, traffic makes getting to work easy. Working with great people and a company that cares about individuals makes staying at work enjoyable.\"<strong>-Eric M.</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-pushpinder.heer-small.png\" alt=\"Pushpinder H.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n<td>The team comradery that exists at ATS is like no other. Employees at every level truly love and understand their role.<strong>-Pushpinder H., Software Engineer III</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>I like working for ATS because upper management really wants to create something useful for the customer. They genuinely want to solve real problems for the Navy,not just make money. That makes me feel good about working here.<strong>- Rick W., Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>I like working at ATS because the CEO is such a great guy<strong></strong><strong>- Rick L., President &amp; CEO</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-rick.leenstra-small.png\" alt=\"Rick L.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-bob.lawing-small.png\" alt=\"Bob L.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n<td>\"They look out for their troops; they are straight forward and honest. Management is good at acquiring work.\"-<strong>Bob L., Senior Configuration Specialist</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>\"I love being able to be myself, yet always being challenged to better myself.\"<strong>- Aaron M., Software Engineer</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-aaron.moore-small.png\" alt=\"Aaron M.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #3c3c3c;\"><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-eric.portney-small.png\" alt=\"Eric P.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #3c3c3c;\">\"ATS has assembled a dynamic, experienced group of individuals who understand how to work together as a team, how to approach problems in innovative ways, and who arent afraid to try bold solutions.\"</span><strong>- Eric P., Proposal Coordinator</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p align=\"left\">\"ATS has the funniest, most interesting white boards of anywhere I\'ve worked. Where else would you find a white board showing the design for a flux capacitor?\"</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><strong>- Bryan B., Software Engineer</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-bryan.benson-small.png\" alt=\"Bryan B.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-lacy.dove-small.png\" alt=\"Lacy D.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n<td>\"The diversity of my work allows me to work with many people, across several projects, covering a wide array of tasks so Im seldom bored. We like to work, learn and socialize together... and that makes all the difference.\"<strong>- Lacy D., Senior Project Coordinator</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>\"As an ATS employee, you are part of the family.\"<strong>- Dennis W., Director</strong></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/testimonial-dennis.wilkelis-small.png\" alt=\"Dennis W.\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>\"Working at ATS has put me in direct contact with not only some of the finest minds working in technology today, but also some of the finest people you would ever want to meet. Cutting edge thinkers meet cutting edge technology, what\'s better than that?\"<strong>- Devin W., Systems Administrator</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','Employee Testimonials','','inherit','open','open','','346-revision-v1','','','2014-08-06 18:42:38','2014-08-06 18:42:38','',346,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/08/06/346-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(531,3,'2014-08-06 18:43:05','2014-08-06 18:43:05','<p><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/G5Zf08Kp2o8\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Learn about what ATS is doing, in the words of our employees, to help our customers leverage their data to make better decisionsfaster and smarter.</span></p>\r\n<h3>Start your experience at ATS today!</h3>\r\n<p><a style=\"color: #8a2216;\" href=\"http://atsid.hrmdirect.com/employment/job-opening.php?req=81262&amp;&amp;nohd#job\"><img src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/atsid-button-apply.png\" alt=\"Apply\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\r\n','Working with ATS','','inherit','open','open','','348-revision-v1','','','2014-08-06 18:43:05','2014-08-06 18:43:05','',348,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/08/06/348-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(532,3,'2014-08-06 18:49:53','2014-08-06 18:49:53','<h2>Why Applied Technical Systems?</h2>\r\n<p><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-127 alignleft\" src=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/meet-ats-image-300x216.jpg\" alt=\"meet-ats-image\" width=\"300\" height=\"216\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: #000000;\">Applied Technical Systems Inc. (ATS) isan expert in cloud-based software solutions, lifecycle support solutions, data analytics, data mining and data visualization.We institute agile software development with user-centered design.<a title=\"Our Solutions\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/our-solutions/\">Learn more about our solutions &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"color: #000000;\">Founded in1980, ATS has helped government agencies and commercial clients arrive at better decisions through intelligent discovery solutions, total life cycle expertise for the US Navy, and a broad range of systems engineering services. ATS clients include the U.S. Intelligence Community, Department of Commerce, Department of Homeland Security, and the Department of Defense. Headquartered in Silverdale, WA, ATS also has offices in Alexandria and Suffolk, VA.<a title=\"History\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/meet-ats/history/\">Explore ATS History &gt;&gt;</a></p>\r\n<div id=\"block-system-main\" class=\"block block-system block-main block-system-main even block-without-title\" style=