nects and visualizes disparate life cycle data to help decision makers drive system performance.</p>\n<h3><a title=\"Discovery and Decision Support\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/services/it-services/\">Discovery &amp; Decision Support</a></h3>\n<p>Are you frustrated with searching for value in large data sets? Do you spend a significant amount of time building complex data queries that dont find what youre looking for? Local or clouArcus data analytics software can help - even in the cloud.</p>\n<h3><a title=\"Custom Software Development\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/services/software-development/\">Custom Software Development</a></h3>\n<p>ATS offers systems integration and custom software development that range from Web portals to data mining applications. Using agile software development we create user-centered designs that will enhance your business workflow.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','Services','','inherit','open','open','','25-autosave-v1','','','2014-10-08 16:55:16','2014-10-08 16:55:16','',25,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/09/16/25-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(609,3,'2014-09-16 23:57:26','2014-09-16 23:57:26','<p>ATS designs and develops custom software solutions that create direct connections between your data and your goals. We help organizations integrate, analyze and visualize the data they need to power optimal performance, operational readiness and intelligent decisions.</p>\r\n<p>We are an experienced, cohesive team uniquely suited to resolving sophisticated business intelligence challenges from data engineering and analytics through user-centered interface design.</p>\r\n<p>ATS can help you realize value faster with our proven, proprietary technology framework and agile software development practices. However, the word agile describes more than just our approach to software development. Its the way we understand and respond to customers needs.</p>\r\n<h2>Integrated Logistics Support</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Discovery &amp; Decision Support</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Custom Software Development</h2>\r\n<p>ATS offers systems integration and custom software development that range from Web portals to data mining applications. Using agile software development we create user-centered designs that will enhance your business workflow.</p>\r\n<h3>Agile Software Development</h3>\r\n<p>By taking the time to understand a clients problem better than anyone else, we see connections between data and decisions that others might overlook. While most want to know what a client wants their custom software to do with data, ATS wants to know why. Rather than assume we already have the answer, our team stays focused on asking the right questions to ensure we create the most useful and scalable application possible.</p>\r\n<p>ATS has streamlined custom software development with a time-tested framework of interconnected technologies. In the hands of our talented team, we leverage our innovations to design and deliver scalable data integration, analysis and visualization solutions with utmost control over cost, timeline and quality.</p>\r\n<h3>Data Analytics and Management</h3>\r\n<p>We specialize in helping customers extract valuable information from complex, high-volume databases, and have developed several groundbreaking, patented data analytics software technologies in this area.</p>\r\n<h2></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">MSAT is a tool that connects and visualizes disparate life cycle data to help decision makers drive system performance.</span></p>','Services','','inherit','open','open','','25-revision-v1','','','2014-09-16 23:57:26','2014-09-16 23:57:26','',25,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/09/16/25-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(610,3,'2014-09-17 00:02:47','2014-09-17 00:02:47','<p>Keeping ships ready since 1980</p>\r\n<h2>ATS is focused on innovative and sustainable integrated logistic support and lifecycle support solutions.</h2>\r\n<p>For over 30 years, ATS has focused on the development of innovative and sustainable maintenance and lifecycle solutions to product lifecycle system support problems. From the outset, our emphasis has been on finding ways to make the products of the Navys logistics lifecycle support system work for, rather than against, the shipboard maintenance technician.</p>\r\n<p>Most Operational Availability (Ao) and system sustainability problems experienced by the fleet today can be traced to a failure somewhere in the shore-based lifecycle logistics support system. Lack of onboard repair parts (OBRP) supply support is a particularly acute system sustainability problem, but there are also systemic problems with technical manuals, drawings, configuration and other types of engineering technical data. In many cases these technical data problems are the root cause of OBRP support problems, but they are often perceived as a Supply support problem.<img class=\"alignright wp-image-249 size-full\" src=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/lss_index.jpg\" alt=\"Keeping ships ready since 1980\" width=\"213\" height=\"142\" /></p>\r\n<p>ATS uses our unique product lifecycle maintenance solutions to troubleshoot and correct lifecycle integrated logistics support and sustainability problems. Most of our Maintenance Support Group technicians are former Navy technicians who have extensive experience in the operation and maintenance of the full spectrum of shipboard systems. This maintenance-oriented perspective is fundamental to our view of the integrated logistics support world and our maintenance support analysis processes.</p>\r\n<p>We train our maintenance support technicians using our own in-house lifecycle support management training program which we developed from years of hands on experience in all facets of the integrated logistics support system. The end result is an experienced shipboard maintenance technician who is also trained to troubleshoot and repair any element of the Navys integrated logistics support system to make sure the ILS system provides o