 Performance.</li>\r\n<li><b>Reduce Overhead of Compilation by 75%</b>- Combined with data automatically ingested into Crew Quiz, performance metrics and analyses are only a click away.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://atsid.com/sites/default/files/request-demo2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"45\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>For more information:</strong></p>\r\n<p>email:<a class=\"mailto\" href=\"mailto:crew-atlas@atsid.com\">crew-atlas@atsid.com</a></p>\r\n<p>phone: 253.514.2432</p>\r\n<p>View: <a href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/ATS-CrewAtlas-FS.pdf\">Crew Atlas Fact Sheet</a></p>\r\n<p>View:<a href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/wp-content/uploads/ATS-CrewQuiz-FS.pdf\">Crew Quiz Fact Sheet</a></p>\r\n<div><a style=\"color: #8a2216;\" href=\"http://atsid.com/contact-us?interest=crew-atlas\">Contact ATS today</a>to see a live demo of Crew Quiz.</div>\r\n</div>','Crew Quiz','','inherit','open','open','','203-revision-v1','','','2014-10-08 17:18:04','2014-10-08 17:18:04','',203,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/10/08/203-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(721,3,'2014-10-08 18:08:26','2014-10-08 18:08:26','<h2>We design intuitive interfaces, scalable architectures, productive software, clean APIs and, above all, beautiful experiences.</h2>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<p>Applied Technical Systems has been designing and developing innovative software for over 30 years. Our success comes from our highly skilled and dedicated team\'s focus on excellence in four key disciplines.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>UX Design</strong></h3>\r\n<p>People are complicated, but software doesn\'t have to be. Effortless user experiences come from true understanding. We get that.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\"><i class=\"ic ui\"></i>\r\n<h3><strong>UI Design</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Pixel perfect interfaces, every time. Were all about the details. We create rich, responsive, beautiful interfaces.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\