o 20 months.</p>\r\n<p>With over 8,000 patent examiners using a complex business process, ATS approached the problem by designing and developing a state of the art user interface, built on open source technologies, that allows examiners to personalize the application to the way they do their work.</p>\r\n<p>Additionally, ATS has architected a gadget-based platform that enables information to be shared between components to reduce redundancies and allow for the application to act intelligently based on the users previous actions.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','UI / UX Design','','inherit','open','open','','653-revision-v1','','','2014-10-08 18:08:26','2014-10-08 18:08:26','',653,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/10/08/653-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(722,3,'2014-10-08 18:09:19','2014-10-08 18:09:19','<h2>We design intuitive interfaces, scalable architectures, productive software, clean APIs and, above all, beautiful experiences.</h2>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<p>Applied Technical Systems has been designing and developing innovative software for over 30 years. Our success comes from our highly skilled and dedicated team\'s focus on excellence in four key disciplines.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>UX Design</strong></h3>\r\n<p>People are complicated, but software doesn\'t have to be. Effortless user experiences come from true understanding. We get that.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\"><i class=\"ic ui\"></i>\r\n<h3><strong>UI Design</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Pixel perfect interfaces, every time. Were all about the details. We create rich, responsive, beautiful interfaces.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\"><i class=\"ic dev\"></i>\r\n<h3><strong>Development</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Our programmers craft elegant APIs using a variety of high-productivity and high-performance open technologies. <a href=\"http://github.com/atsid\">We ? open source.</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\"><i class=\"ic 