y based on the context of words in the indexed corpus. The important data is brought to the users attention with easy to understand visual cues. Stop searching and start discovering with data analytics software solutions that make sense.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Arcus Search\" href=\"http://dev.atsid.com/products/arcus-search/\">Arcus Concept Search</a></p>\r\n<p>Arcus Concept Search assists the user in constructing a data query based on the context of words in the indexed corpus. The important concepts are brought to the users attention by providing visual cues and returning data results that are highly relevant  dramatically reducing the time spent in search.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Discovery and Decision Support','','inherit','open','open','','195-revision-v1','','','2014-10-10 17:53:43','2014-10-10 17:53:43','',195,'http://dev.atsid.com/2014/10/10/195-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(724,3,'2014-10-10 17:57:16','2014-10-10 17:57:16','<h2>Structured &amp; Unstructured Data Analytics with Arcus Cloud Analytical Platform</h2>\r\n<div id=\"block-system-main\" class=\"block block-system block-main block-system-main even block-without-title\">\r\n<div class=\"block-inner clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"content clearfix\">\r\n<article id=\"node-basic-page-98\" class=\"node node-basic-page node-published node-not-promoted node-not-sticky author-ebendesign odd clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"content clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"field-items\">\r\n<div class=\"field-item even\">\r\n<p>ATS has developed a groundbreaking cloud-based data analytics platform built on our patented data analytics technology. Our engine ingests and normalizes disparate data sources to create a data structure that facilitates powerful pattern matching and relationship discovery. This service-enabled platform is extensible through v